# Cloudflare redirects for Narramorph.
#
# This site is served via Cloudflare Workers Static Assets, whose _redirects file
# accepts ONLY relative, same-host URLs. Cross-host canonicalization
# (www.narramorph.com -> narramorph.com, 301) is therefore configured as a
# zone-level Redirect Rule in the Cloudflare dashboard (Rules -> Redirect Rules),
# not here — see docs/RELEASE_ROLLBACK.md section 1. A cross-host rule in this file
# fails the deploy with "Only relative URLs are allowed" [code 100324].
#
# The app is hash-routed (#/passage/:id), so all real navigation is under "/", which
# serves index.html; genuinely unknown paths fall through to the branded 404.html.
# No SPA rewrite or same-host redirect is needed, so this file is intentionally
# comment-only.
